Package project1

Class EventCalendar

java.lang.Object
project1.EventCalendar
public class EventCalendar extends Object
This class stores event objects in an array and offers methods to interact with and print the array. An instance of this class holds an array of events and the number of events in the array. The class implements different sorting algorithms for the array of events
Author:
Donald Yubeaton, Micheal Kassie
